{"tid":2412844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實整個\"全心向黨, 政治領悟力高\"商戶list有無得諗???","createTime":"2021-02-18T09:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T15:48:12.000Z","uid":345137,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bde223087a5d977cd378729c00849e5cdd12401f","tid":2412844,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T09:15:40.000Z","msg":"而家開始睇到有D商戶<br />\n<br />\n1. 即使個客拒絕, 依然用威脅之勢去叫個客裝APP<br />\n2. 唔裝app既客填完資料, 商戶積極討論, 更主動索取 主動查證同核對個客資料<br />\n<br />\n黨要求一, 佢地自己識做到十, 可見商戶旗幟鮮明, 政治執行力比其他商戶更高, <br />\n對香港人統戰不遺餘力<br />\n<br />\n點都要幫呢D全心向黨, 政治領悟力高既商戶整返個LIST表揚下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360fd26ef56603b9622751bc989ed467ac3dfe42","tid":2412844,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T09:18:04.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"19b8262fc3ef380ec1d1c514bed539087de55277","tid":2412844,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T09:23:05.000Z","msg":"自推."},{"pid":"75c333e89d87c5aaf90082b177abf4b76de7adac","tid":2412844,"uid":370061,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T09:24:22.000Z","msg":"值得推<br />\n愛共好商戶名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081c454bb3624dc3fca9c3447822dcf5558fb07c","tid":2412844,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T09:47:20.000Z","msg":"再推~"},{"pid":"a81cd4f8e85346d0c418b8b376b9e1515cb3ae87","tid":2412844,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:33:56.000Z","msg":"又推~"},{"pid":"d5e776663a71553b525a1ba874f7a3c1c6f21eff","tid":2412844,"uid":109985,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:40:39.000Z","msg":"大部分藍都唔係愛國愛黨<br />\n入咗list大把藍都未必會去"},{"pid":"b466369d05597ae08af7199ad96a24590509fd8d",